{"tid":2392796,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【利鎮】樓價低至70萬有交易","createTime":"2021-02-03T04:34:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T05:36:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f58521bf6ae8bbc323e7afba3434080f9942cf7a","tid":2392796,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T04:34:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/GBZSMFXZPBHLHEV2MLG3LZMQSA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FGBZSMFXZPBHLHEV2MLG3LZMQSA%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrUaSLYUUk8srzc0BovwEr9s%3D&h=9aef3ad3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FGBZSMFXZPBHLHEV2MLG3LZMQSA%2F&h=38ebec77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/GBZSMFXZPBHLHEV2MLG3LZMQSA/</a><br />\n<br />\n【利鎮】樓價低至70萬有交易<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fyyQ036ZTXSkXk5wAfaAUF1pgNw=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GPETZBCRYRHSXFHXFNVDNSGXTU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfyyQ036ZTXSkXk5wAfaAUF1pgNw%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGPETZBCRYRHSXFHXFNVDNSGXTU.jpg&h=8e9cfca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■住在利鎮的Mandy認為，由這裏出城上班很方便。<br />\n<br />\n不少人討論移民，都提起曼徹斯特（Manchester，下稱曼城）或利物浦，除了沃靈頓外，還有其他市鎮環繞這兩個城市，例如Mandy就住在利鎮（Leigh），屬於大曼徹斯特郡（Greater Manchester），樓價低至70萬多港元便有交易，出入曼城、利物浦僅約40分鐘。她認為利鎮生活機能不錯，與住在曼城相比，「除咗要揸車出入，無咩大分別。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【卡迪夫】空氣水質佳 物價較低<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曼城文職機會多<br />\n<br />\n利鎮離沃靈頓北方不遠處，車程不足半小時，離曼城稍近，「揸車出曼城大約30至40分鐘，去利物浦45分鐘左右。」Mandy指，住在利鎮而出城上班，「好方便亦好普遍。」<br />\n<br />\n綜合英國賣樓網站資料，以。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【倫敦】侍應、售貨員有力置業<br />\n<br />\nMandy指，有時她會到倫敦辦公，故對利鎮與城市的分別感受較深，「city同town最大分別就係悶，亞洲人都較少，大。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n要在郡內找工作，曼城的機會較多，尤其文職。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"d4396d9925276656b2c6bdaee25956e58917f482","tid":2392796,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T05:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}